---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 143
By: Swami Ramdas
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Eluding the Ego
  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Destruction of I-Consciousness
---
The only thing which a man must renounce if he wishes to attain the Supreme
Truth is the notion of individuality -- nothing else.
